data.description: Situated in the heart of Crawford, this home offers a rare opportunity to embrace the small-town charm. With this home recent remodel in 2023 you can enjoy the modern feel this home provides coupled with the rustic charm of Crawford. The kitchen is a beautiful blend of modern and rustic with countertops and open shelves made of live edge wood from a local sawmill just outside of town. Detached garage (19'10"x23'6") with a workshop (29'5"x15'7") attach to the back of the garage. The home and garage are located on .52 Acer corner lot giving anyone more than enough room for gardens or equipment to be stored on the property. This amazing home is just waiting for you!
